race.description: Summerland Trophies Country Boosted Maiden Handicap
race.comment: COPENHAGEN CAT (8) speedy mare starting to hit her straps at the last two outings. Jumped in trip when taking control early before tiring to run third over 1210m at this track. Well drawn today and will prove hard to get past. ROCK ON ANGEL (3) is yet to break through in six runs. Finished fifth at her last appearance over 1015m at Grafton on October 28. Finds a suitable assignment this time and is a great chance to break through. DANDEELION WISHES (9) best effort in four career starts when she gripped on late to secure third over 1015m at Grafton. Maps well and ready to peak. OUTOFTHEOFFICE (2) lightly raced gelding resuming. Back without a trial and gave a glimpse of what he's capable of when second at Grafton two runs back. Gets the right set-up and can shed his maiden status.
